com.identityx.clientSDK.base

Class RestClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.identityx.clientSDK.base.RestClient

  • public class RestClient
extends Object
    This class is used to perform the calls to the Rest service. It uses Jackson to serialize/deserialize Java objects to the JSON format to be passed further to/from a HttpClientRequestExecutor
